  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3 resubmission)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This resubmission elevates the Model Risk Level to 3 following regulatory feedback that the decision consequence warrants higher scrutiny. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are fully assessed and meet required levels. The 'Equivalency of input parameters' factor is documented as not requiring assessment because the modelling team judged it inapplicable to a purely computational sensitivity study; however, the factor is carried with factorStatus 'not-assessed' rather than 'not-applicable', leaving a material gap at MRL 3.",
