    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are assessed and all meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 3. The equivalency of input parameters factor is documented as not applicable to a computational sensitivity study and was not formally assessed. The team accepted the overall credibility evidence as sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision that the CFD model identifies worst-case hemolysis operating conditions within the stated acceptance criterion (RH < 1).",
